</SP>
<SP>
<SPEAKER>PROTHEUS.</SPEAKER>
<P>Why? Could'&s;t thou perceive &s;o much from her?</P>
</SP>
<SP>
<SPEAKER>SPEED.</SPEAKER>
<L>Sir, I cou'd perceive nothing at all from her:</L>
<L>No, not &s;o much as a Ducat for delivering your Letter:</L>
