</SP>
<SP>
<SPEAKER>SERVANT.</SPEAKER>
<P>The&s;e were his very Words.</P>
</SP>
<SP>
<SPEAKER>EXTON.</SPEAKER>
<L>"Have I no Friend?"&mdash;quoth he; he &s;pake it twice</L>
<L>And urg'd it twice together; did he not?</L>
</SP>
