<SPEAKER>SERVANT.</SPEAKER>
<P>He did.</P>
</SP>
<SP>
<SPEAKER>EXTON.</SPEAKER>
<L>And &s;peaking it, he wi&s;tly look'd on me,</L>
<L>As who &s;hall &s;ay&mdash;I would thou wert the Man,</L>
<L>That would divorce this Terror from my Heart;</L>
