</SP>
<STAGE><PB N="119" REF="120"><HI>Scene changed to the Pri&s;on at</HI> Pomfret.</STAGE>
<STAGE><HI>Enter to the</HI> KING <HI>the</HI> KEEPER <HI>with a Di&s;h.</HI></STAGE>
<SP>
<SPEAKER>KEEPER.</SPEAKER>
<P>Fellow, give place; here is no longer Stay.</P>
</SP>
