<L>If I die not to-day with <HI>Frenchmen</HI>'s Rage,</L>
<L>To-morrow I &s;hall die with mickle Age;</L>
<L>By me they nothing gain; and if I &s;tay,</L>
<L>'Tis but the &s;hortening of my Life one Day.</L>
<L>In thee thy Mother dies our Hou&s;hold's Name</L>
<L>My Death's Revenge, thy Youth and <HI>England</HI>'s Fame:</L>
